UID:azure-client-secret-rotation-18m-lb-kc-bp058@lianabanyan.com
SUMMARY:🔑 Azure Client Secret Rotation Due (Liana Banyan Code Signing)
DESCRIPTION:The Azure client secret for code signing expires ~18 months after creation.\nRotate it now to maintain uninterrupted GitHub Actions signing.\n\nSteps:\n1. Log into Azure Portal (portal.azure.com)\n2. Navigate to: Entra ID → App Registrations → liana-banyan-code-signing-sp\n3. Certificates & Secrets → New Client Secret\n   - Description: github-actions-signing-rotated-<YYYYMM>\n   - Expiry: 18 months\n4. COPY the new Value immediately (shown only once)\n5. Go to: GitHub → LianaBanyanPlatform → Settings → Secrets → Actions\n   - Update AZURE_CLIENT_SECRET with the new value\n6. Back in Azure Portal: DELETE the old client secret\n7. Trigger a manual workflow_dispatch of release-sign.yml to verify\n\n⚠️ Do NOT delete old secret BEFORE updating GitHub Secret.\n⚠️ Do NOT let the secret expire — signing pipeline will break immediately.\n\nCanon ref: azure-signing-setup.md §6 · docs/reminders/ · K-C BP058 W6
LOCATION:portal.azure.com
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-P14D
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:14 days until Azure client secret rotation due — schedule time now
END:VALARM
